The Federal Government has appointed Adeboye Mustapha Zubair as the acting rector of Auchi Polytechnic, Auchi in Edo state.
   
A statement signed by the institution’s Public Relations Officer, Mustapha Oshiobugie, said Zubair, until his appointment, was the institution’s Deputy Rector in charge of Administration.  To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .